      "tag": "heading",
      "text": "Typography"
    },
    {
      "tag": "text",
      "text": "Standard paragraph text renders cleanly with system fonts and comfortable line height."
    },
    {
      "tag": "text",
      "text": "- Bullet point items begin with a dash"
    },
    {
      "tag": "text",
      "text": "- Each item renders with a clean dot marker"
    },
    {
      "tag": "text",
      "text": "- Lists support unlimited depth and length"
    },
    {
      "tag": "text",
      "text": "* Asterisk bullets also work identically"
    },
    {
      "tag": "text",
      "text": "> Blockquotes are prefixed with the greater-than symbol and render with a left accent border."
    },
    {
